Complete eyering without the 'tear' shape like Pacific-slope, olive greenish crown and back, yellowish throat and front, buffy upper wingbar, pale buffy lower wingbar, pale yellow edges on secondaries do not reach the lower wingbar, moderate primary projection.  Did not bob the tail when perched like PSFL normally do.  Responded to calls.  Photos.

Photo by Bill Chen.
